    "description": "经典与现代的结合<br>受《金属弹头》和《崩溃堡垒》等经典动作游戏的启发，《艾利欧斯的狩猎》提供了探索机制、掌握游戏和通过游戏感受自己实际进展的经验。所有这些都采用了现代方法以达到流畅的游戏性、精美的图形和尖端的技术。<br><br>追逐你的梦想<br>在一个赏金猎人被视为维护秩序的英雄的异世界里，年轻的Zelicyan人艾利欧斯梦想成为他们中的一员。但他必须克服自己种族的弱点和渺小，才能实现他的梦想。在你作为艾利欧斯的旅程中，你将面对来自大自然的怪物，变异的生物，嗜血的部落，自然现象等等。为了扳回一局，你将不得不使用你所掌握的一切，包括几种武器、装备，当然也包括升级你自己和你的无人机。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/8554f6f414fc313b8f702c4981a8916d.poster.avif?t=1669716548\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/8554f6f414fc313b8f702c4981a8916d.webm?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/8554f6f414fc313b8f702c4981a8916d.mp4?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>最重要的特点<br>射击和装置相结合，挑战性和奖励性并存的游戏玩法。<br>流畅的控制和灵敏的反应能帮助你更好的掌握游戏。<br>手工制作和动作捕捉的混合动画使角色动作更自然，让你始终处于控制状态。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/e3c6f272a78bc6d3e8730e6b597fb975.poster.avif?t=1669716548\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/e3c6f272a78bc6d3e8730e6b597fb975.webm?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/e3c6f272a78bc6d3e8730e6b597fb975.mp4?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>时间目标为硬核玩家提供了疯狂的体验。<br>探索独特而充满敌意的外星科幻环境。<br>在你从“弱小和缓慢”到“致命和老道”的过程中不断提高技能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/3b676581f1d233581d3526c1d5e2b1df.poster.avif?t=1669716548\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/3b676581f1d233581d3526c1d5e2b1df.webm?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867800/extras/3b676581f1d233581d3526c1d5e2b1df.mp4?t=1669716548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
